item.title: Transcript of the phone conversation with the FBI’s Field Office of Chicago
item.description: Transcript of the phone conversation between me and the FBI’s Field Office of Chicago. I called them on December 23, 2015, at 20:30 (8:30pm) Beijing time.

item.title: F.B.I. Chicago answers the victim asking him to please contact the FBI's Public Access Line
item.description:
On 2015-12-18, I receive an answer from the Intake Unit of the Field Office of the F.B.I. in Chicago.

FROM : Chicago@ic.fbi.gov

To: Vincent B. Le Corre

SUBJECT: RE: McDonald’s massive fraud in Europe

item.title: Email sent to the F.B.I. Washington Field Office on December 16, 2015. McDonald’s Corporation.
item.description:
This email was sent to the F.B.I. Washington D.C. Field Office on December 16, 2015 at 15:00 Beijing time.

FROM : [Whistle-blower’s email address] Visit X-v-France.com for more information about me

TO : washington.field@ic.fbi.gov

SUBJECT: McDonald’s massive fraud in Europe
